OL,7,FThree police officers who confronted
OL,8,FSouthport knife attacker Axel
OL,9,FRudakubana have been nominated for
OL,10,Fbravery awards.
OL,12,FSergeant Gregory Gillespie, Constable
OL,13,FLuke Holden and PCSO Timothy Parry
OL,14,Fwere the first officers to arrive on
OL,15,Fthe scene of the attack at the Taylor
OL,16,FSwift-themed workshop on 29 July 2024.
