OL,4,CSouthport attacker nominated for
OL,5,Cbravery awards
OL,7,FRudakubana, 18, who murdered Alice da
OL,8,FSilva Aguiar, nine, Bebe King, six,
OL,9,Fand Elsie Dot Stancombe, seven, and
OL,10,Finjured 10 others, was confronted by
OL,11,Fthe officers as he stood at the top of
OL,12,Fa flight of stairs holding a large
OL,13,Fknife.
OL,15,FThe three men have been nominated for
OL,16,Fthe National Police Bravery Awards
OL,17,F2025 after facing what Merseyside
OL,18,FPolice Chief Constable Serena Kennedy
OL,19,Fdescribed as "unimaginable horror".
