OL,7,FMs Kennedy said: "As first on the
OL,8,Fscene and in those frantic initial
OL,9,Fmoments, they were unaware of the
OL,10,Fhorrific events taking place but they
OL,11,Fdismissed any thoughts for their own
OL,12,Fsafety, bravely detaining the offender
OL,13,Fwhile protecting and helping the
OL,14,Fvictims and those inside.
OL,26,@oD@ROU
