OL,3,CThree officers who confronted
OL,4,CSouthport attacker nominated for
OL,5,Cbravery awards
OL,7,F"We are all immensely proud of Ps
OL,8,FGillespie, Pc Holden and PCSO Parry
OL,9,Ffor their courage, professionalism and
OL,10,Fswift actions in such horrendous
OL,11,Fcircumstances. For the officers to be
OL,12,Frecognised in this way is true
OL,13,Ftestament to them all."
OL,15,FAccording to the nomination, Mr
OL,16,FGillespie was first to arrive at Hart
OL,17,FStreet after a radio call at midday to
OL,18,Freports of a male attacking children
OL,19,Fwith a knife.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@WO]
