OL,7,FHe described seeing "chaos" when he
OL,8,Farrived and directing paramedics to a
OL,9,Fseriously injured child.
OL,11,FHe was joined by Mr Holden and Mr
OL,12,FParry and the officers witnessed
OL,13,Fmembers of the public running away
OL,14,Ffrom the dance studio carrying young
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,FArmed with a baton and a Taser, Mr
OL,18,FGillespie and Mr Holden entered the
OL,19,Fbuilding, while Mr Parry covered the
OL,20,Fexit, and found Rudakubana holding a
OL,21,Flarge knife at the top of the stairs.
