OL,7,FThe officers approached the suspect,
OL,8,Fwhile shouting at him to drop the
OL,9,Fknife, and Mr Parry ran in to assist.
OL,11,FRudakubana, who was jailed for a
OL,12,Fminimum of 52 years in January,
OL,13,Fdropped the knife and, after officers
OL,14,Fstruck him with a baton and kicked him
OL,15,Fto get him under control, was
OL,16,Fhandcuffed and arrested.
