OL,7,FMerseyside Police Federation chairman
OL,8,FChris McGlade said: "Police officers
OL,9,Fjoin the service to keep our
OL,10,Fcommunities safe and prevent them from
OL,11,Fharm.
OL,13,F"In the face of the most challenging
OL,14,Fand perilous of circumstances, these
OL,15,Fthree officers exemplified this
OL,16,Fcommitment.
