OL,7,F"Without hesitation, they prioritised
OL,8,Fpublic safety and demonstrated the
OL,9,Fhighest levels of bravery. Their
OL,10,Fprofessionalism was unparalleled, and
OL,11,Fit is fitting that we acknowledge and
OL,12,Fhonour their actions accordingly."
OL,14,FThe Police Bravery Awards will be held
OL,15,Fon July 10.
